            . I am a cheesemonger. On Sunday morning, the 24th of May, I saw the prisoner come out of Mr. Lord's house, with the candles in a bag, about nine o'clock. My father thought it strange that they should be taken out on Sunday, and informed Mr. Lord.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180617-14-person152">
                  WILLIAM 
                  DRINKWATER
               <interp inst="t18180617-14-person152" type="surname" value="DRINKWATER"></interp>
